title: 哼哼 你猜錯了 這次是名言佳句分享

content.author: 沒台大法_誓不為人
content.body:
Inspirational Quotes 經典佳句

生命要往回看才懂意義，但是要往前進才有意義
Life can only be understood backwards;but it must be lived forwards.

人生沒有十全十美
Do it or do not do it,you will regret both.

可憐之人必有可恨之處，反之亦同
If I am the chief of sinners,I am the chief of sufferers also.

逆境之中必有轉機
The bargain might appear unequal;but there was still another consideration in the scales.

雞鳴不已於風雨，松柏後凋於歲寒
Quiet minds cannot be perplexed or frightened but go on in fortune or misfortune at their own private pace, like a clock during a thunderstorm.
